query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('electronics')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('adc',
'analog',
'audio',
'avr',
'circuit-design',
'filter',
'fpga',
'integrated-circuit',
'motor',
'power-electronics',
'pwm',
'relay',
'transformer');
